reviewText: This guy makes my face hurt!
Supposedly "Like New". Visible fingermarks and scratches. DVD froze multiple times. My wife liked the show though.

Saw Michael in Dublin and so wanted to buy his DVD but he only has Region 2!  Sorry but I'm not buying a European DVD player to watch your DVD.  Have you considered coming to America?  Loved your show.
Good album. Couldn't play it on Blue Ray/DVD Player though. Genre great, music fit my needs and moods. Album arrive well before estimated time and in god condition.
